```
┌─────────────────────┬─────────────────┬──────────────────────┐
│ Situation           │ Thread State    │ What CPU Does        │
├─────────────────────┼─────────────────┼──────────────────────┤
│ Thread.sleep()      │ TIMED_WAITING   │ runs other threads   │
│ File read/write     │ BLOCKED         │ runs other threads   │
│ Network call        │ BLOCKED         │ runs other threads   │
│ DB query            │ BLOCKED         │ runs other threads   │
│ synchronized lock   │ BLOCKED         │ runs other threads   │
│ wait()              │ WAITING         │ runs other threads   │
│ join()              │ WAITING         │ runs other threads   │
│ Heavy computation   │ RUNNING         │ busy on this thread  │
│ GC pause            │ all BLOCKED     │ runs GC thread       │
└─────────────────────┴─────────────────┴──────────────────────┘
```

